'''快速存取记录器'''（{{lang-en|quick access recorder}}，缩写'''QAR'''）是一种机载[[飛行紀錄儀|飞行数据记录仪]]，设计目的是提供快速、方便的方式存取原始飞行数据<ref name="FAA-FOQA">{{Cite web|url=http://www.ihst.org/portals/54/Attachment%20D_AC120-82.pdf|title=Advisory Circular - Flight Operational Quality Assurance|accessdate=10 October 2011|date=4 December 2004|publisher=U.S. Department of Transportation - Federal Aviation Administration|page=5|archive-date=2019-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190712095745/http://www.ihst.org/portals/54/Attachment%20D_AC120-82.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>，例如通过[[通用串行總線|USB]]<ref name="L3microQAR">{{Cite web|url=http://www.l-3ar.com/PDF_Files/MKT063_mQAR.pdf|title=Micro Quick Access Recorder|accessdate=10 October 2011|last=L-3 Communications|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120303003129/http://www.l-3ar.com/PDF_Files/MKT063_mQAR.pdf|archivedate=2012年3月3日}}</ref>或[[蜂窝网络|蜂窝网络]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.teledyne.com/news/groundlink.asp|title=Teledyne Controls Announces Successful Launch of Wireless GroundLinkTM|accessdate=10 October 2011|publisher=Teledyne|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120425060030/http://www.teledyne.com/news/groundlink.asp|archivedate=2012年4月25日|df=}}</ref>连接，和/或使用标准[[記憶卡|記憶卡]]<ref name="L3microQAR">{{Cite web|url=http://www.l-3ar.com/PDF_Files/MKT063_mQAR.pdf|title=Micro Quick Access Recorder|accessdate=10 October 2011|last=L-3 Communications|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120303003129/http://www.l-3ar.com/PDF_Files/MKT063_mQAR.pdf|archivedate=2012年3月3日}}</ref>。QAR常被[[航空公司|航空公司]]用于提高[[飞行安全|飞行安全]]和运行效率，通常属{{tsl|en|Flight_operations_quality_assurance|飞行品质监控}}计划的一部分。<ref>{{Cite book|url=http://www.gao.gov/products/RCED-98-10|title=Efforts to Implement  Flight Operational  Quality Assurance  Programs|date=December 1997|accessdate=10 October 2011|page=4|author=General Accounting Office|archive-date=2020-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201114234126/https://www.gao.gov/products/RCED-98-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>与飞机的[[飛行紀錄儀|飞行数据记录仪]]（FDR）相同，QAR从[[飞行数据采集单元|飞行数据采集单元]]（FDAU）接收输入，记录超过2000项飞行参数。<ref name="FAA-FOQA">{{Cite web|url=http://www.ihst.org/portals/54/Attachment%20D_AC120-82.pdf|title=Advisory Circular - Flight Operational Quality Assurance|accessdate=10 October 2011|date=4 December 2004|publisher=U.S. Department of Transportation - Federal Aviation Administration|page=5}}</ref>QAR可使用比FDR更高的采样率，并且在某些情况下记录周期更长。与FDR不同的是，QAR通常不是国家民用航空管理局要求的商业航班必备设备，并且不是为事故调查所设计。尽管如此，部分QAR曾在事故中幸存，并且提供了FDR记录范围外的有价值信息。<ref>http://www.ntsb.gov {{Wayback|url=http://www.ntsb.gov/ |date=20141213052941 }} National Transportation Safety Board</ref>

